looking for you, Ms. Honey.

25:49.516 --> 25:51.518
[ SIGHS ]

25:51.518 --> 25:55.255
[ BEEP ]

25:55.255 --> 25:57.724
♪♪♪♪

25:57.724 --> 25:59.660
HM.

25:59.660 --> 26:03.469
SHE'S SERIOUS.

26:03.469 --> 26:06.006
