27:42.175 --> 27:43.343
CANDACE?

27:43.343 --> 27:44.945
YES.

27:44.945 --> 27:46.513
CALLING THE POLICE?

27:46.513 --> 27:48.481
YES.

27:48.481 --> 27:51.017
AND?

27:51.017 --> 27:55.822
I ‐‐ AND FOR
SECOND‐GUESSING YOU.

27:55.822 --> 27:58.224
AND?

27:58.224 --> 28:02.703
UH, AND FOR NOT
