28:21.988 --> 28:23.524
PERFECT.

28:23.524 --> 28:25.291
THAT'S PERFECT.

28:25.291 --> 28:28.361
ARE YOU SURE YOU...

28:28.361 --> 28:29.863
YES, YOU ARE.

28:29.863 --> 28:31.331
YES.

28:31.331 --> 28:33.099
OKAY.

