IN THE OVAL AND HAVE A DRINK.

28:45.579 --> 28:48.248
I WOULD LIKE THAT.

28:48.248 --> 28:50.183
I LOOK FORWARD TO IT.

28:50.183 --> 28:55.188
♪♪♪♪

28:55.188 --> 28:56.823
OH, IS THERE
ANYTHING ELSE YOU NEED?

28:56.823 --> 28:58.559
NO.
YOU SURE?

28:58.559 --> 29:00.661
[ LAUGHS ] YES, I'M SURE.

29:00.661 --> 29:03.670
NOW, IF YOU DON'T MIND,
I'D LIKE TO CALL IT.

29:03.670 --> 29:06.172
OF COURSE.

29:06.172 --> 29:12.979
♪♪♪♪

29:12.979 --> 29:14.147
[ BEEP ]

29:14.147 --> 29:16.149
[ Line ringing ]

29:16.149 --> 29:17.984
CANDACE: Hello?
HELLO.

29:17.984 --> 29:20.587
Hi.
HEY. HOW ARE YOU?

29:20.587 --> 29:24.591
I'm interested.
WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

29:24.591 --> 29:29.262
Why are you calling me?
TO CHECK ON YOU.

29:29.262 --> 29:34.034
Well, all right.
YOU'RE DOING OKAY?

29:34.034 --> 29:38.805
I'm on my way to a funeral home.
You tell me how I'm doing.

29:38.805 --> 29:41.341
WELL, I CAN IMAGINE
YOU'RE ANGRY...

29:41.341 --> 29:45.445
AND SAD,
AND PROBABLY ANNOYED.

29:45.445 --> 29:49.215
Good choice.
You nailed all of them.

29:49.215 --> 29:52.118
CANDACE, I'M SORRY.

29:52.118 --> 29:56.022
I know you just wanted
to check in, but I'm fine.

29:56.022 --> 29:57.891
OKAY.

29:57.891 --> 29:58.925
I need to go.

29:58.925 --> 30:00.460
WILL YOU CALL ME LATER?

30:00.460 --> 30:01.635
I don't know.

30:01.635 --> 30:03.904
WELL, I'LL WAIT
FOR YOUR CALL.

30:03.904 --> 30:05.672
I'LL BE FREE AFTER 11:00,
YOUR TIME.

30:05.672 --> 30:06.807
♪♪♪♪

30:06.807 --> 30:08.308
[ Receiver clicks ]

30:08.308 --> 30:11.177
[ BEEP ]

30:11.177 --> 30:19.653
♪♪♪♪

30:19.653 --> 30:21.622
COME RIGHT THIS WAY,
PLEASE.

30:21.622 --> 30:29.495
♪♪♪♪

30:29.495 --> 30:37.370
♪♪♪♪

30:37.370 --> 30:45.245
♪♪♪♪

30:45.245 --> 30:47.514
ARE YOU READY
TO VIEW THE BODY?

30:52.285 --> 30:55.622
NO. CAN WE JUST
TALK FIRST, PLEASE?

30:55.622 --> 30:56.990
OKAY.

30:56.990 --> 31:00.126
SO, WE HAVE THIS CASKET
AND THIS ARRANGEMENT.

31:00.126 --> 31:02.769
MS. CRYER HAS INSTRUCTED ME THAT
SHE WILL BE PAYING FOR THIS,

31:02.769 --> 31:04.370
SO THIS IS THE ONE
THAT YOU CHOSE?

31:04.370 --> 31:05.572
YES.

31:05.572 --> 31:09.910
SHE DID SAY THAT
MONEY WASN'T A PROBLEM.

31:09.910 --> 31:11.812
THIS IS THE ONE.
BUT THIS IS MUCH NICER.

31:11.812 --> 31:16.683
EXCUSE ME.
THIS IS GONNA BE THE ONE.

31:16.683 --> 31:18.218
YES, SIR.

31:18.218 --> 31:21.555
WE ALSO HAVE SOME
FUNERAL PROGRAMS PRINTED.

31:21.555 --> 31:23.890
THIS IS
THE ORDER OF SERVICE.

31:26.527 --> 31:28.995
YES.

31:28.995 --> 31:31.097
OKAY. NOW, THIS IS
A HARD QUESTION,

31:31.097 --> 31:33.466
BUT WOULD YOU LIKE
THE CASKET OPEN OR CLOSED?

31:33.466 --> 31:35.401
OPEN.
WAIT.

31:35.401 --> 31:38.471
WHAT, BENNY?

31:38.471 --> 31:39.573
HOW DOES THIS ‐‐
HOW DOES...

31:39.573 --> 31:41.842
OH, WE'LL MAKE SURE
HE LOOKS GOOD.

31:44.410 --> 31:45.646
LORD, I DIDN'T EVEN
THINK ABOUT THAT.

31:45.646 --> 31:47.480
WE'LL MAKE SURE.

31:47.480 --> 31:49.950
DO YOU THINK WE SHOULD
KEEP IT CLOSED?

31:49.950 --> 31:51.184
IF YOU PREFER.

31:51.184 --> 31:54.154
OPEN.

31:54.154 --> 31:57.791
I WANT EVERYBODY TO SEE
WHAT THEY DID TO THAT BABY.

31:57.791 --> 32:01.234
I WANT EVERYBODY TO SEE
WHAT THOSE THUGS DID TO HIM,

32:01.234 --> 32:04.004
WHAT GUNS ARE DOING TO US.

32:04.004 --> 32:07.974
SO, OPEN?

32:07.974 --> 32:09.843
YES, SIR.

32:09.843 --> 32:11.978
NOW, WHEN WE START
THE SERVICE, YOUR PASTOR,

32:11.978 --> 32:13.079
REVEREND DANIELS...

32:13.079 --> 32:16.082
[ DOOR CLOSES ]
...WILL COME IN AND...

32:16.082 --> 32:19.285
♪♪♪♪

32:19.285 --> 32:21.221
HELLO.

32:21.221 --> 32:25.425
♪♪♪♪

32:34.334 --> 32:36.036
THIS IS MY SISTER.

32:36.036 --> 32:38.772
HI, I'M JONATHAN WILSON,
THE FUNERAL DIRECTOR.

32:38.772 --> 32:40.106
I'M CANDACE.

32:40.106 --> 32:42.676
SHE'S HIS MOTHER.
I'M SORRY.

32:42.676 --> 32:46.112
I KNOW THAT THIS IS
AN ESPECIALLY HARD TIME FOR YOU

32:46.112 --> 32:47.447
AND YOUR FAMILY RIGHT NOW.

32:47.447 --> 32:48.982
YOU HAVE NO IDEA.

32:48.982 --> 32:51.117
NO, I DON'T.

32:51.117 --> 32:53.353
BURYING A CHILD
IS ALWAYS HARD.

32:53.353 --> 32:55.656
IT'S THE PART OF MY JOB
I DISLIKE THE MOST.

32:55.656 --> 32:58.759
CANDACE.

32:58.759 --> 33:02.435
WE PICKED THE CASKET OUT.

33:02.435 --> 33:05.271
WHO CHOSE IT?

33:05.271 --> 33:08.274
MOMMY.

33:08.274 --> 33:10.110
I DON'T LIKE IT.
I WANT THE BLUE ONE.

33:10.110 --> 33:12.846
CANDACE...
I WANT THE BLUE ONE.

33:12.846 --> 33:16.049
WELL...
I WANT THE BLUE.

33:16.049 --> 33:17.818
WELL...
THE BLUE ONE IS MORE EXPENSIVE,

33:17.818 --> 33:20.521
AND WE ALREADY
CHOSE THIS ONE.

33:20.521 --> 33:23.023
IT SHOULD BE BLUE.
HE LIKED BLUE.

33:23.023 --> 33:26.059
HOW DO YOU KNOW
WHAT HE LIKED?

33:26.059 --> 33:27.994
I WANT HIM
IN THE BLUE ONE.

33:27.994 --> 33:29.229
YOU GOT THE MONEY
TO PAY FOR IT?

33:29.229 --> 33:31.765
DO YOU?

33:34.000 --> 33:39.339
SIR, I CHOSE THIS ONE,
AND THIS IS THE ONE.

33:39.339 --> 33:42.275
AND, SIR, I WANT HIM
IN THE BLUE ONE.

33:42.275 --> 33:47.013
CANDACE, MOMMY
ALREADY CHOSE ONE.

33:47.013 --> 33:48.481
AND I'M HIS MOTHER.

33:48.481 --> 33:50.784
I KNOW THAT, AND I KNOW
THIS IS HARD FOR YOU.

33:50.784 --> 33:54.187
THIS IS HARD FOR ALL OF US.
I DON'T CARE!

33:54.187 --> 33:55.789
CANDACE, WE DON'T
HAVE MONEY FOR THIS.

33:55.789 --> 33:57.057
THIS IS TWICE ‐‐
YOU'RE NOT HEARING ME!

33:57.057 --> 33:58.491
YES, I AM.

33:58.491 --> 34:00.667
NO. LISTEN.

34:04.571 --> 34:06.507
MAYBE I CAN MAKE SOME CALLS

34:06.507 --> 34:08.474
AND SEE WHAT KIND OF
DISCOUNT WE CAN GET.

34:08.474 --> 34:10.777
I DON'T CARE WHAT KIND
OF DISCOUNT YOU GET.

34:10.777 --> 34:12.846
THIS IS THE ONE.

34:12.846 --> 34:14.781
GO MAKE THE CALLS.

34:14.781 --> 34:17.483
OKAY. WELL,
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

34:21.087 --> 34:22.255
DON'T DO THIS HERE.

34:22.255 --> 34:24.257
I'M NOT DOING ANYTHING.

34:24.257 --> 34:25.892
I'M JUST TRYING
TO BURY MY SON.

34:25.892 --> 34:27.761
AND NOW YOU WANT
TO STEP IN.

34:27.761 --> 34:29.696
DON'T YOU DARE.

34:29.696 --> 34:31.598
WE'RE NOT DOING THIS.

34:31.598 --> 34:33.399
YOU WENT INTO
THE BATHROOM WITH HIM,

34:33.399 --> 34:36.136
AND YOU DIDN'T COME OUT
WITH A SCRATCH.

34:36.136 --> 34:38.104
THIS IS NOT TIME
NOR THE PLACE FOR THIS.

34:38.104 --> 34:40.440
HOW DID YOU
NOT GET SHOT?

34:40.440 --> 34:42.275
CANDACE, YOU'RE SAYING
THAT LIKE YOU WANTED HER TO.

34:42.275 --> 34:44.410
WELL?

34:44.410 --> 34:47.180
YOU SHUT YOUR MOUTH.
YOU SHUT UP NOW.

34:47.180 --> 34:50.250
YOU DIDN'T PROTECT HIM.

34:50.250 --> 34:52.753
YOU DID THIS TO SPITE ME.

34:56.623 --> 34:58.592
YOU DID!

34:58.592 --> 35:00.867
YOU DID.

35:03.069 --> 35:06.039
YOU WANTED TO HURT ME
TO GET EVEN WITH ME.

35:09.275 --> 35:12.579
YOU JUST WANT ME TO SAY
THAT YOU WERE RIGHT.

35:14.915 --> 35:17.350
CANDACE, STOP.
JUST STOP THIS.

35:17.350 --> 35:18.685
SHE DIDN'T HELP HIM.

35:18.685 --> 35:20.253
THE HELL SHE DIDN'T!

35:20.253 --> 35:22.088
I WAS THERE. I WATCHED IT.

35:22.088 --> 35:23.924
AND SHE DONE MORE
THAN YOU EVER HAVE.

35:26.126 --> 35:27.260
WHAT?
YEAH, THAT ENOUGH.

35:27.260 --> 35:30.230
I'M SICK OF YOUR BULL...
ALL YOU BRING IS BULL...

35:30.230 --> 35:32.866
I WAS THERE WHEN WAR CAME
IN THERE LOOKING FOR YOU.

35:32.866 --> 35:36.136
ALL RIGHT? HE COULD'VE KILLED US
ALL BECAUSE OF WHAT YOU DID.

35:36.136 --> 35:37.638
HOW CAN YOU NOT
SEE THAT, CANDACE?

35:37.638 --> 35:39.072
YOU DON'T SEE THAT?

35:39.072 --> 35:41.575
SHE'S RIGHT. WHY DO YOU
ALWAYS HAVE TO BE RIGHT?

35:41.575 --> 35:43.677
MOMMY'S RIGHT.

35:43.677 --> 35:45.946
YOU DO THE SAME THING
OVER AND OVER.

35:45.946 --> 35:47.280
IT'S ALWAYS THE SAME
THING WITH CANDACE,

35:47.280 --> 35:49.249
OVER AND OVER,
EXPECTING A NEW RESULT.

35:49.249 --> 35:51.017
THAT'S CRAZY.
IT'S INSANITY.

35:51.017 --> 35:53.086
I DON'T EVEN GET THAT.
SHE DIDN'T DO NOTHING.

35:53.086 --> 35:54.487
SHE WOULD'VE DIED
TO PROTECT THAT BABY.

35:54.487 --> 35:57.190
I WATCHED HER. SHE ALMOST DIED
PROTECTING YOUR SON.

35:57.190 --> 35:59.459
I TELL YOU WHAT. I'M NOT HEARING
ONE MORE MINUTE OF THIS

35:59.459 --> 36:01.101
COMING OUT OF YOUR MOUTH.
I'M SICK OF IT.

36:01.101 --> 36:03.637
I'M SICK OF YOU!

36:06.272 --> 36:07.240
WHAT?

36:07.240 --> 36:10.711
YOU ‐‐ YOU!
I'M SICK OF YOU.

36:10.711 --> 36:12.412
YOU HAVE BEEN
DEPENDING ON ME

36:12.412 --> 36:15.081
FOR EVERYTHING SINCE
I'VE BEEN ON MY OWN!

36:15.081 --> 36:17.618
CANDACE WHO ‐‐
WHO ARE YOU TALKING TO?

36:17.618 --> 36:21.154
YOU! I'M TALKING TO YOU,
CALLING ME FOR MONEY,

36:21.154 --> 36:23.924
TELLING ME
YOUR FAIRY‐TALE DREAMS

36:23.924 --> 36:26.860
AND HOW EXPENSIVE
THINGS WERE!

36:26.860 --> 36:28.461
SO, WHAT YOU THINK ‐‐
YOU THINK I WAS BEGGING YOU?

36:28.461 --> 36:29.863
YES, YOU WERE BEGGING!
YOU WERE BEGGING ME!

36:29.863 --> 36:31.297
NO, I'M NOT. I'M NOT
BEGGING YOU, ALL RIGHT?

36:31.297 --> 36:34.701
I'M TALKING TO MY SISTER,

36:34.701 --> 36:36.036
SOMEONE WHO LOVES ME,
ALL RIGHT?

36:36.036 --> 36:38.539
I LOVE YOU, AND THAT'S WHY I
TALK TO YOU ABOUT THESE THINGS.

36:38.539 --> 36:41.307
I DON'T GOT NOBODY
TO TALK TO.

36:41.307 --> 36:43.476
SO I SHARE MY DREAMS
WITH YOU.

36:47.614 --> 36:52.352
AIN'T NOBODY TELL YOU TO SELL
YOUR ASS TO HELP ME GET IT!

36:52.352 --> 36:54.287
I SEE YOU'VE BEEN
TALKING TO YOUR MOTHER.

36:54.287 --> 36:56.222
NO, DON'T YOU REMEMBER?
CANDACE, WE TALKED.

36:56.222 --> 36:58.692
YOU TOLD ME THIS.

36:58.692 --> 37:01.500
WONDER WHY I EVEN TRY.
WONDER WHY.

37:01.500 --> 37:03.637
YEAH, YOU KNOW WHAT?
I ASK MYSELF THE SAME THING.

37:03.637 --> 37:06.305
WHY AM I EVEN TRYING?
I SHOULD LISTEN TO MOMMY.

37:06.305 --> 37:08.742
AND THIS WHOLE GAME, TRYING TO
FLIP IT AROUND ON ME AND HER,

37:08.742 --> 37:10.043
IT AIN'T WORKING
HERE NO MORE.

37:10.043 --> 37:14.080
IT AIN'T WORKING.

37:14.080 --> 37:15.549
DO YOU HAVE THE INVOICES?

37:15.549 --> 37:17.651
I'M SORRY.
I SPOKE WITH MY PARTNER,

37:17.651 --> 37:20.020
AND SHE SAID THE PRICE
IS WHAT IT IS.

37:20.020 --> 37:23.456
WE CAN'T DO ANYTHING.
IT'S OUR MOST POPULAR.

37:23.456 --> 37:26.259
OKAY. UM, I STILL
WANT THE BLUE ONE.

37:26.259 --> 37:27.894
SHOULD I BILL
MRS. CRYER FOR THIS?

37:27.894 --> 37:29.262
NO.

37:29.262 --> 37:31.832
MRS. CRYER?

37:31.832 --> 37:34.467
SHE'S PAYING
FOR THE FUNERAL?

37:34.467 --> 37:36.537
WHO ELSE DO YOU THINK
HAS THAT KIND OF MONEY?

37:38.839 --> 37:40.907
SHE'S NOT PAYING
FOR MY SON'S FUNERAL.

37:40.907 --> 37:43.977
[ SCOFFS ]

37:43.977 --> 37:47.781
‐YOU GOT $6,000, CANDACE?
‐SHE'S NOT.

37:47.781 --> 37:49.415
I'LL GET IT TO YOU.

37:49.415 --> 37:51.852
WELL, THE FUNERAL
IS TOMORROW.

37:51.852 --> 37:53.319
WE HAVE TO HAVE
PAYMENT TODAY.

37:53.319 --> 37:55.856
DO YOU HAVE
A CREDIT CARD?

37:55.856 --> 37:57.390
I'LL BRING YOU CASH.

37:57.390 --> 38:01.167
SIR. WE'RE GONNA BURY HIM, OKAY?
SHE'S NOT BRINGING ANYTHING.

38:01.167 --> 38:02.435
SHUT UP!
CANDACE...

38:02.435 --> 38:04.304
THIS IS MY SON.

38:04.304 --> 38:06.472
AND I DECIDE
WHAT'S BEST FOR HIM.

38:08.975 --> 38:10.977
CANDACE, THEY WANT
THE MONEY NOW.

38:10.977 --> 38:13.413
HOW YOU GONNA GET
THE MONEY NOW, HUH?

38:13.413 --> 38:15.415
HMM? ANSWER ME!

38:19.820 --> 38:23.356
THAT MAN WHO'S
RUNNING FOR PRESIDENT.

38:23.356 --> 38:26.627
WHAT?

38:26.627 --> 38:30.396
I SAW HIM ON THE NEWS,

38:30.396 --> 38:32.666
TALKING ABOUT HOW
HIS HEART WENT OUT TO US

38:32.666 --> 38:35.902
'CAUSE HE KNOWS THE FAMILY.

38:35.902 --> 38:37.838
SHE'S PROBABLY
BLACKMAILING HIM.

38:37.838 --> 38:43.043
♪♪♪♪

38:43.043 --> 38:45.345
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT? WHAT?

38:45.345 --> 38:48.448
THAT'S WHY
THE SECRET SERVICE, BENNY.

38:48.448 --> 38:50.283
THAT'S WHY YOU
WERE IN JAIL.

38:54.087 --> 38:55.321
WHAT?

38:55.321 --> 38:57.457
OH, DON'T ACT LIKE
YOU DON'T KNOW.

38:57.457 --> 38:59.325
I DON'T KNOW WHAT
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

38:59.325 --> 39:02.869
SHE IS BLACKMAILING HIM.

39:06.740 --> 39:10.544
I'LL TAKE THE BLUE ONE.

39:10.544 --> 39:13.013
SO YOU DON'T WANT TO TAKE
THE GIFT OF MONEY.

39:13.013 --> 39:17.217
YOU'D RATHER GO AND STEAL
TO BURY YOUR BABY?

39:17.217 --> 39:18.619
AND YOU'D RATHER
TAKE THE CRUMBS

39:18.619 --> 39:21.354
THAT FALL FROM TABLES
OF WHITE PEOPLE,

39:21.354 --> 39:24.024
WOULDN'T YOU, MISS HANNA?

39:24.024 --> 39:25.358
THAT'S ENOUGH.

39:25.358 --> 39:26.660
GO STEP AND FETCH IT
OVER THERE.

39:26.660 --> 39:28.895
I'M TAKING CARE OF MYSELF.

39:28.895 --> 39:30.230
SIR, WE'RE GONNA, UH ‐‐

39:30.230 --> 39:31.698
WE'RE GONNA KEEP THE
ARRANGEMENTS AS THEY ARE.

39:31.698 --> 39:34.400
WHERE WILL HE BE BURIED?
AT DEGAR.

39:37.237 --> 39:40.641
NO. HE'LL BE
BURIED AT SIMMS.

39:40.641 --> 39:43.510
‐DO YOU HAVE A PLOT THERE?
‐I WILL GET ONE.

39:43.510 --> 39:47.480
‐WELL, THAT WILL TAKE TIME.
‐I WILL GET ONE.

39:47.480 --> 39:51.317
WE'VE SCHEDULED SERVICE
FOR TOMORROW.

39:51.317 --> 39:55.889
WHO SCHEDULED IT?
YOUR MOTHER. RIGHT?

39:55.889 --> 39:58.792
WHAT A MOTHER SHE IS.

39:58.792 --> 40:00.360
MAN.

40:00.360 --> 40:04.270
HE WILL BE BURIED AT SIMMS.

40:04.270 --> 40:07.040
AND HIS FUNERAL
WILL NOT BE TOMORROW.

40:07.040 --> 40:10.443
IT'LL BE THURSDAY.

40:10.443 --> 40:13.213
OKAY.

40:14.480 --> 40:16.750
I'LL BRING YOU
THE MONEY TOMORROW.

40:16.750 --> 40:19.019
OKAY.
ARE YOU OKAY WITH THIS?

40:19.019 --> 40:22.322
DON'T YOU ASK HER
ANOTHER THING ABOUT MY SON.

40:22.322 --> 40:25.726
YES, MA'AM.

40:25.726 --> 40:27.961
AND WHAT IS THIS?

40:27.961 --> 40:29.896
THIS IS THE PROGRAM
YOUR MOTHER CAME UP WITH.

40:29.896 --> 40:31.632
OH. NO, NO.

40:31.632 --> 40:34.300
NO, NO.
CANDACE, CANDACE.

40:34.300 --> 40:37.504
NO, MA'AM.

40:37.504 --> 40:41.908
HE WILL NOT BE
BURIED IN A CHURCH.

40:41.908 --> 40:43.677
HE'LL BE BURIED AT SIMMS.

40:47.781 --> 40:54.354
MY SON WILL BE BURIED IN THIS
ONE AND NOT IN THIS THING.

40:54.354 --> 40:55.522
OH, MY GOD.

40:55.522 --> 40:57.123
AAH!

40:57.123 --> 40:59.926
WHOA, WHOA WHOA.
WHOA, WHOA. SHH.

40:59.926 --> 41:00.934
AAH!

41:00.934 --> 41:02.435
[ SOBS ]

41:02.435 --> 41:05.238
MS. YOUNG, I'M SORRY.

41:05.238 --> 41:08.308
CANDACE, THIS IS WHY WE CAME
HERE, TO VIEW THE BODY.

41:08.308 --> 41:09.409
‐DON'T TOUCH ME!
‐I'M SORRY. I AM SORRY.

41:09.409 --> 41:12.513
TO FINALIZE EVERYTHING,
CANDACE.

41:12.513 --> 41:16.449
[ SOBS ]

41:16.449 --> 41:18.585
COUNSELOR, IS
THERE ANYTHING ELSE?

41:18.585 --> 41:21.655
<i>NEXT ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

41:21.655 --> 41:24.791
THE LORD GIVETH,
AND THE LORD TAKETH AWAY!

41:24.791 --> 41:27.127
YOU CAN HAVE YOUR SON!

41:27.127 --> 41:30.430
NOW, WHEN WILL YOU UNDERSTAND?
MEN DON'T HAVE BRAINS.

41:30.430 --> 41:32.699
WE ARE THEIR BRAINS.

41:32.699 --> 41:34.701
I NEED YOU TO GET THAT.

41:34.701 --> 41:36.837
I CAN'T LET YOU SPEND
A LOT OF MONEY ON ME.

41:36.837 --> 41:38.471
YES, YOU CAN. I WILL.

41:38.471 --> 41:40.140
ACCORDING TO MY MATH,
YOU STILL OWE ME

41:40.140 --> 41:41.441
A WHOLE LOT OF SEX, GIRL.

41:41.441 --> 41:44.310
3029, SHOULD YOU
DECIDE YOU'D LIKE

41:44.310 --> 41:46.012
TO START
MAKING RESTITUTION.

41:46.012 --> 41:47.047
I'VE HAD ENOUGH OF YOU.

41:47.047 --> 41:48.815
WHAT YOU GONNA DO,
LITTLE GIRL?

41:48.815 --> 41:51.151
YOU GONNA SHOOT ME
WITH YOUR LITTLE GUN?

41:51.151 --> 41:52.986
OOH! GRAB ME, GIRL.
GRAB MY $4,000 SUIT.

41:52.986 --> 41:54.755
LET GO. LET GO.
GRAB IT!

41:54.755 --> 41:57.691
I'LL SHOW YOU HOW MUCH
BLACK LIVES MATTER.
